==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disedge
<hw>Dis*edge"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To deprive of an
edge; to blunt; to dull.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Served a little to <qex>disedge</qex>⟦br⟧
The sharpness of that pain about her heart.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disedify</ent>⟦br⟧
